  Kinetic (Delta T^0):                   1.168460794884042         31.7954           733.22          3067.79
  Delta V^Pauli Coulomb:                -0.701322072283232        -19.0839          -440.09         -1841.32
  Delta V^Pauli LDA-XC:                 -0.224521218010104         -6.1095          -140.89          -589.48
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Exchange:            0.044758964169184          1.2180            28.09           117.51
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Correlation:        -0.028858883341135         -0.7853           -18.11           -75.77
                                      --------------------     -----------       ----------      -----------
  Total Pauli Repulsion:                 0.258517585418756          7.0346           162.22           678.74
 (Total Pauli Repulsion =
  Delta E^Pauli in BB paper)

